  "prompt": "What's the average number of answers to each question on Quora?",
  "response": "The average number of answers to each question on Quora typically varies. There is no fixed number, as it depends on several factors, including the popularity of the question, the topic it falls under, and how engaged the Quora community is with it. Some questions might receive hundreds of answers, while others might only have a few or even none. However, generally speaking, many questions tend to receive a handful to a dozen answers.",
